# Atomic-write temp files. Tools/editors create files like
# `account.html.tmp.34428.4cee44dfc561` during saves, then rename them away.
# On Windows, `vercel dev`'s file watcher crashes with a libuv assertion
# (UV_HANDLE_CLOSING) when it tries to watch one of these as it disappears.
# These should never be deployed regardless.
*.tmp.*
*.tmp

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
